  "text": "Recent studies have shown similar event rates after normal SPECT in diabetics compared with non-diabetics [CITATION_1] , although balanced triple-vessel disease is more common in diabetics [CITATION_2] and thus may cause underestimation of functional ischaemia on SPECT.",
